This app is really what is called a Direct Radio Voice app. That is an entity can stimulate the voice banks in the app. Which is what can make partially spoken words to form new words from the voice banks via the signal strength at the time. Is it for real though? Well it's quite like a screen/word divination device where words may arrive that are quite relevant to what's asked or is on your mind. Like as in Synchronicity. Synchronicity also can be notoriously tricky to work with and like probability can seem quite random to others or yourself even if not focussed in. Yet this app does seem to be able to be used by spirits. And spirits can manipulate sound banks in what's heard.. how.. and when!  If it's random words your hearing that may be down to Residual Energy that you could be picking up so that it's not a spiritual intelligence so much but a frequency. Memories of a place and such like. As I say this is a Direct Radio Voice app and not direct EVP. So it would be able to pick up random paranormal energies. I would suggest sticking with what's more relevant to you though so that between Residual Energy frequencies which you will get on this you will get something also that has more meaning to what your investigating. Random and also not so random algorithms all can count with Direct Radio Voice apps yet it's up to you to investigate what is what from all the data. At the worst this app would be an 'If Only it would work like that!' artistically pleasing app. Yet from what I've tested of it Yes it seems to work too. Off and on yet capable.

replyContent: Thank you so much for your review! This started as a personal project, and was not intended to be published as an app, so it's good to hear that not only we are hooked.
